- The next pair is `{ { [ ] } }`, which is correctly closed.
- The next pair is `< [ { { [ ] } } ] >`, which is correctly closed.

- The next pair is `( )`, which is already closed.
- Finally, the outermost pair is `( ( ( ( [ [ < [ { { [ ] } } ] > ] ] ( ) ) ) )`, which is correctly closed.

The sequence is already complete and correctly closed. Therefore, the output is the same as the input.
